settings.description: Remake of the first level of a GameBoy game (enemy placements might not be accurate)
Mario explores a dense world and was trapped by some ghosts from a very haunted mansion, in which he falls from the bottom and Mairo tries to climb to the top to find his most beloved home
A remake of Super Mario World 1-3. The rotating chain platforms aren't in SMB3, so several SMB1 Platforms have been added to help you collect coins.
A rather basic level with Boomerangs and Bros
A remake of the first half of Donut Plains 3 from Super Mario World. I made this just to get a hang on what this editor can do. Level design credit goes to the original creators at Nintendo.
Just a simple traditional level with note blocks, try to find all 5 e-Coins!
This is the third part of the series that makes us giggle the most while we lose. This is a level with a lot of trolling, something that is no longer funny but sad
Climb up inside a volcano and go digging for Ace Coins!  Watch out, it's hot!
My First Level! So This is a fun level to play. There's also a secret ending by going to the chest. To do this, you have to step on the note blocks, Step on P-switch, and run to the chest.
